w construction) by the bank does not exceed:</p><ul><li>378,120 euros for houses in the Flemish <strong>Region</strong></li><li>434,830 euro for houses in listed <a href=\"https://www.vlaamswoningfonds.be/sites/default/files/inline-files/Overzicht%20gemeenten%20verhoogde%20verkoopwaarde.pdf\">municipalities with a higher average sales value</a>.</li></ul>",
